---
import LandingPageLayout from '../layouts/LandingPageLayout.astro';
---

<LandingPageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Ontario Condo Guide."
  path="/privacy"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
>
  <div class="prose max-w-2xl">
    <p>
      Ontario Condo Guide respects your privacy. This policy describes what information we collect,
      how we use it, and the choices you have.
    </p>
    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>
      If you contact us through the contact form, we collect your name, email address, role, topic,
      and message so we can respond to your inquiry.
    </p>
    <p>
      Like most websites, our hosting infrastructure may log standard technical data such as IP
      address, browser type, and pages visited.
    </p>
    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <p>
      We use contact submissions to reply to questions about our educational resources. We do not
      sell personal information.
    </p>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      We may use privacy-conscious analytics to understand how visitors use the site and improve
      our content. Analytics data is aggregated and does not identify individual visitors.
    </p>
    <h2>Questions</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, use the <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</LandingPageLayout>
